title: #92Noon! Greenway/Everett/Birk
description: PA & Nordo are live from day one of the fair!  Chad Greenway joins the show to talk about the Vikes and his new app, Tatum Everett of the Vikings Entertainment Network continues the Purple and Gold convo, and Matt Birk makes his weekly appearance!
